	<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Nos encontramos</span> <span class="hps">ya en pleno</span> <span class="hps">2015 y</span> <span class="hps">queremos</span> <span class="hps">explicaros</span> <span class="hps">cu&aacute;les son nuestros</span> <span class="hps">planes para</span> <span class="hps">este a&ntilde;o</span> <span class="hps">en <a href="http://barcelona.goteo.org/">Goteo</a></span><a href="http://barcelona.goteo.org/"> <span class="hps">Barcelona.</span></a> <span class="hps">A estas alturas ya</span> <span class="hps">mucha</span> <span class="hps">gente</span> <span class="hps">sab&eacute;is que</span> <span class="hps">la tarea que</span> <span class="hps">hacemos desde</span> <span class="hps">Goteo</span> <span class="hps">y la <a href="http://fuentesabiertas.org/">Fundaci&oacute;n</a></span> desde la <span class="hps">que gestionamos</span> <span class="hps">nuestra plataforma</span> <span class="hps">va m&aacute;s</span> <span class="hps">all&aacute; de facilitar</span> <span class="hps">una herramienta</span> <span class="hps">de financiaci&oacute;n</span><span>:</span> <strong><span class="hps">creemos en</span> <span class="hps">el poder</span> <span class="hps">del hecho</span> </strong><span class="hps"><strong>colectivo</strong>,</span> <span class="hps">enfocando</span> <span class="hps">parte de nuestra</span> <span class="hps">labor</span> <span class="hps">en facilitar</span> <span class="hps">la mutualizaci&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">de recursos y</span> <span class="hps">beneficios que</span> <span class="hps">proyectos</span> <span class="hps">de sectores</span> <span class="hps">o tem&aacute;ticas</span> <span class="hps">muy diversas</span> <span class="hps">pueden ofrecer.</span><br />
	<br />
	<span class="hps">En esta l&iacute;nea,</span> <span class="hps">ofrecemos</span> <span class="hps">ayuda</span> <span class="hps">a</span> <span class="hps">cada</span> <span class="hps">impulsor</span> <span class="hps">en la definici&oacute;n del</span> <a href="https://goteo.org/discover/view/fulfilled"><span class="hps">retorno</span> <span class="hps">colectivo</span></a> <span class="hps">de sus proyectos</span> <span class="hps">y el conocimiento</span> <span class="hps">de las diversas</span> <span class="hps">alternativas</span> <span class="hps">de licencias</span> <span class="hps">libres</span><span class="hps">/</span><span class="hps">abiertas</span> <span class="hps">existentes</span><span>, si es necesario</span> <span class="hps">con</span> <span class="hps">ayuda</span> <span class="hps">de expertos</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>como</span> <a href="http://xnet-x.net/contactanos-para/portal-de-cultura-libre/"><span class="hps">X.net</span></a><span>,</span> <a href="http://guifi.net/"><span class="hps">Guifi.net</span></a> <span class="hps">o</span> <a href="http://www.consumocolaborativo.com/"><span class="hps">Consumo</span> <span class="hps">Co</span><span class="hps">laborativo</span></a><span>)</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">De esta manera cada</span> <span class="hps">impulsor</span> <span class="hps">genera un</span> pedazo <span class="hps">m&aacute;s</span> <span class="hps">de espacio</span> <span class="hps">libre</span> <span class="hps">en la red,</span> <span class="hps">permitiendo</span> <span class="hps">mayor impacto</span> <span class="hps">social mediante</span> <span class="hps">la generaci&oacute;n de <strong>valor</strong></span><strong> </strong><span class="hps"><strong>de uso</strong>,</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">anteponiendo</span> <span class="hps">el bien com&uacute;n</span> <span class="hps">al lucro</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">la privatizaci&oacute;n.</span> <span class="hps">Esta l&iacute;nea</span> <span class="hps">es la base</span> <span class="hps">de nuestra</span> <span class="hps">apuesta por</span> <a href="https://goteo.org/blog/4621"><span class="hps">proyectos</span> <span class="hps">c&iacute;vicos,</span> <span class="hps">&eacute;ticos,</span> <span class="hps">colaborativos</span> <span class="hps">y</span> </a><span class="hps"><a href="https://goteo.org/blog/4621">abiertos</a>.</span><br />
	<br />
	<strong><span class="hps">#AperitiusCrowd</span> </strong><span class="hps">es nuestro</span> <span class="hps">nuevo espacio</span> <span class="hps">de encuentro</span> <span class="hps">bimensual</span> <span class="hps">donde</span><span>, siguiendo los pasos</span> <span class="hps">de la web</span> <a href="http://teamopen.cc/all/"><span class="hps">Team</span> <span class="hps">Open</span></a> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>recopilaci&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">de historias</span> <span class="hps">exitosas</span> <span class="hps">en el uso</span> <span class="hps">de licencias</span> <a href="http://creativecommons.org/"><span class="hps">Creative Commons</span></a><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">queremos destacar</span><strong> <span class="hps">buenas</span> <span class="hps">pr&aacute;cticas</span></strong> <span class="hps">en voz</span> <span class="hps">de impulsores</span> <span class="hps">de proyectos que</span> <span class="hps">nos</span> <span class="hps">gusta</span> <span class="hps">divulgar</span> <span class="hps">porque</span> <span class="hps">encarnan</span> <span class="hps">estos valores</span> <span class="hps">de apertura y</span> <span class="hps">colaboraci&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">en los que</span> <span class="hps">creemos</span><span class="hps">... As&iacute; que</span> <span class="hps">volvemos</span> <span class="hps">con</span> <span class="hps">un nuevo encuentro</span> <strong><span class="hps">el pr&oacute;ximo</span> </strong><span class="hps"><strong>19 de febrero</strong>,</span> <span class="hps">&iexcl;y</span> <span class="hps">con</span> <span class="hps">novedades</span><span>!</span><br />
	<br />
	<span class="hps">Primero</span> <span class="hps">de todo</span><span>, los</span> <span class="hps">#AperitiusCrowd</span> <span class="hps">ser&aacute;n</span> <strong><span class="hps">itinerantes</span></strong><span>:</span> <span class="hps">contaremos</span> <span class="hps">con la colaboraci&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">de diferentes</span> <span class="hps">espacios</span> <span class="hps">de Barcelona que nos</span> <span class="hps">acoger&aacute;n</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">generando</span> <span class="hps">red</span> <span class="hps">con sus diferentes</span> <span class="hps">comunidades.</span> <span class="hps">El primer</span> <span class="hps">#Aperitiu</span> <span class="hps">se llevar&aacute; a</span> <span class="hps">cabo en el</span> <a href="http://barcelona.impacthub.net/"><span class="hps">Impact</span> </a><span class="hps"><a href="http://barcelona.impacthub.net/">Hub</a> de</span> <span class="hps">la Plaza Real,</span> <span class="hps">un inspirador</span> <span class="hps">espacio</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">nodo</span> <span class="hps">barcelon&eacute;s de</span> <span class="hps">la red internacional</span> <span class="hps">de Impact</span> <span class="hps">Hubs</span><span>, que</span> <span class="hps">acoge una</span> <span class="hps">comunidad bien</span> <span class="hps">din&aacute;mica</span> <span class="hps">y centrada en</span> <span class="hps">crear un impacto</span> <span class="hps">positivo</span> <span class="hps">en la</span> <span class="hps">sociedad.</span> <span class="hps">Contaremos con</span> <span class="hps">la presencia</span> <span class="hps">del <a href="http://www.colectivozompopo.org/">Colectivo</a></span><a href="http://www.colectivozompopo.org/"> <span class="hps">Zompopo</span></a><span><a href="http://www.colectivozompopo.org/">,</a> quienes</span> <span class="hps">obtuvieron</span> <span class="hps">15.643<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">&euro;</span></span></span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>de</span> <span class="hps">149</span> <span class="hps">comecenas</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">para su</span> <span class="hps">campa&ntilde;a</span> <a href="https://goteo.org/project/fogones-adobe-nicaragua"><span class="hps">Fogones</span> <span class="hps">mejorados</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">adobe</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">Nicaragua.</span></a> <span class="hps">El equipo de</span> <span class="hps">Zompopo</span><span>, un equipo</span> <span class="hps">transdisciplinar,</span> <span class="hps">generaron</span> <span class="hps">din&aacute;micas</span> <span class="hps">participativas</span> <span class="hps">para el dise&ntilde;o</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">capacitaci&oacute;n en</span> <span class="hps">la autoconstrucci&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">de unos</span> <span class="hps">fogones</span> <span class="hps">que responden a una</span> <span class="hps">problem&aacute;tica</span> <span class="hps">sanitaria</span> <span class="hps">en zonas</span> <span class="hps">de Nicaragua.</span> <span class="hps">En breve</span> <span class="hps">os</span> <span class="hps">informaremos</span> <span class="hps">con m&aacute;s</span> <span class="hps">detalle</span> <span class="hps">pero de momento</span><strong> &iexcl;<span class="hps">reservad la</span> <span class="hps">fecha</span><span>!</span></strong><br />
	<br />
	<span class="hps">Otros espacios</span> <span class="hps">donde tenemos</span> <span class="hps">previsto llevar</span> <span class="hps">los</span> <span class="hps">#Aperitius</span> <span class="hps">son</span> <span class="hps">el <a href="http://ateneusdefabricacio.barcelona.cat/xarxa-de-ateneus-de-fabricacio/ateneu-de-fabricacio-de-les-corts/">Ateneo de</a></span><a href="http://ateneusdefabricacio.barcelona.cat/xarxa-de-ateneus-de-fabricacio/ateneu-de-fabricacio-de-les-corts/"> <span class="hps">Fabricaci&oacute;n de</span> <span class="hps">Les</span> <span class="hps">Corts</span></a><span>, el espai</span> <span class="hps">jove</span> <span class="hps"><a href="http://lafontana.org/">La Fontana</a>,</span> <span class="hps">o el espacio</span> <a href="http://www.grupecos.coop/cat"><span class="hps">ECOS</span></a><span>.</span><br />
	<br />
	<span class="hps">Adem&aacute;s,</span> en los #Aperitius <span class="hps">incluiremos</span> <span class="hps">un espacio</span> <span class="hps">de <a href="http://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pitch"><strong>pitching</strong></a></span> <span class="hps">para la presentaci&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">de vuestros proyectos</span><span>, a fin</span> <span class="hps">de dar a conocer</span> tu<span class="hps"> idea</span> <span class="hps">de campa&ntilde;a</span> <span class="hps">de crowdfunding</span> <span class="hps">y poder</span> <span class="hps">obtener</span> <span class="hps">feedback</span> <span class="hps">de todos los asistentes</span> <span class="hps">al</span> <span class="hps">#</span><span class="hps">Aperitiu,</span> de <span class="hps">los impulsores</span><span>, los</span> <span class="hps">coordinadores de los</span> <span class="hps">espacios</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">del equipo de</span> <span class="hps">Goteo.</span> &iexcl;<span class="hps">Colectivizamos</span> <span class="hps">tambi&eacute;n</span> <span class="hps">el dise&ntilde;o de las</span> <span class="hps">campa&ntilde;as</span> <a href="https://goteo.org/blog/4178"><span class="hps">#Made</span> <span class="hps">in</span> <span class="hps">Goteo</span></a><span>!</span></span> Si te interesa presentar brevemente tu proyecto, escr&iacute;benos a <a href="mailto:barcelona@goteo.org?subject=Pitching">barcelona@goteo.org</a></p>
<p>
	<span lang="es"><span class="hps">Y</span> <span class="hps">con la mirada</span> <span class="hps">puesta en</span> <span class="hps">ampliar</span> <span class="hps">la comunidad</span> <span class="hps">Goteo</span> <span class="hps">para ofrecer</span> <span class="hps">la m&aacute;xima</span> <span class="hps">difusi&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">a las</span> <span class="hps">campa&ntilde;as</span> <span class="hps">que publicamos</span><span>, aparte</span> <span class="hps">de nuestro</span> <span class="hps">creciente</span> <span class="hps">n&uacute;mero</span> <span class="hps">de seguidores</span> <span class="hps">en las redes sociales</span> <span class="hps"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Goteo/268491113192109?ref=tn_tnmn">Facebook</a> y <a href="https://twitter.com/goteofunding">Twitter</a></span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>sumamos</span> <span class="hps">actualmente</span> <span class="hps">m&aacute;s de 28.000</span> <span class="hps">seguidores</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">comentaros</span><span class="hps"> que</span> <span class="hps">nos</span> <span class="hps">hemos</span> <span class="hps">unido a la</span> <a href="http://xes.cat">Xarxa</a><span class="hps"><a href="http://xes.cat"> d&#39;Economia Solid&agrave;ria</a> (XES)</span><span>, que forma parte</span> <span class="hps">de la red</span> <span class="hps">de redes</span> <a href="http://www.economiasolidaria.org/"><span class="hps">REAS</span></a> <span class="hps">as&iacute; como</span> <span class="hps">tambi&eacute;n de su</span> <span class="hps">hom&oacute;loga</span> <span class="hps">a nivel europeo</span> <a href="http://ripess.eu/"><span class="hps">RIPESS</span></a><span>.</span> <span class="hps">All&iacute;</span> <span class="hps">esperamos</span> <span class="hps">aportar nuestro granito</span> <span class="hps">de arena</span> <span class="hps">para el crecimiento</span> <span class="hps">de la <strong>econom&iacute;a</strong></span><strong> <span class="hps">solidaria</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">colaborativa.</span></strong> <span class="hps">Tambi&eacute;n hemos</span> <span class="hps">iniciado</span> <span class="hps">una colaboraci&oacute;n</span> <span class="hps">con el <a href="http://barcelonacultura.bcn.cat/">Institut</a></span><a href="http://barcelonacultura.bcn.cat/"> <span class="hps">de Cultura del</span> <span class="hps">Ajuntament de Barcelona</span></a> <span class="hps">para la</span> <span class="hps">publicaci&oacute;n de los</span> <span class="hps">proyectos</span> <span class="hps">de Goteo</span> <span class="hps">Barcelona</span> <span class="hps">en su <a href="http://barcelonacultura.bcn.cat/crowdfunding">portal web</a></span><a href="http://barcelonacultura.bcn.cat/crowdfunding"> <span class="hps">destinado al</span> <span class="hps">#crowdfunding</span></a><span>.</span><br />
	<br />
	<span class="hps">Seguimos</span><span>, pues,</span> <span class="hps">trabajando</span> <span class="hps">por un</span> <span class="hps">presente y</span> <span class="hps">futuro m&aacute;s</span> <span class="hps">digno</span><span>, m&aacute;s</span> <span class="hps">libre</span> <span class="hps">y m&aacute;s</span> <span class="hps">nuestro</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Es</span> <span class="hps"><strong>de sentido com&uacute;n</strong>.</span></span></p>
